            <p>Digital transformations fail more often than they should. Usually, it's not because of bad technology—it's because the people who understand the business don't speak the same language as the people who build the systems.</p>
            
            <p>We started Tesseract Digital to fix that. Our team has spent years building content systems, implementing analytics infrastructure, and designing semantic architectures for organizations of all sizes. We've seen what works and what doesn't.</p>

            <p>Our approach is straightforward: design systems that make sense for your business, then build them properly. No buzzwords, no unnecessary complexity.</p>
